    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the minimum wage for hgv drivers\r\n \r\n",
        "additional_details": "So in 10 years time the numbers will be far greater, so act now and increase the wage to reflect the work we do on a daily basis and encourage the younger generation to take up a career in driving, because as it stands now I wouldn\u2019t recommend it to",
